OL,3,CFather of murdered schoolgirl Sara
OL,4,CSharif 'attacked in prison'
OL,6,FThe father of Sara Sharif has
OL,7,Freportedly been treated for injuries
OL,8,Fto his neck and face after being
OL,9,Fattacked in prison as ITV News' Ellie
OL,10,FPitt reports
OL,12,FPolice are investigating reports that
OL,13,Fthe father of Sara Sharif has been
OL,14,Fattacked in prison.
OL,16,FUrfan Sharif was allegedly ambushed by
OL,17,Ftwo inmates in a cell at HMP Belmarsh
OL,18,Farmed with the jagged lid of a tuna
OL,19,Ftin on New Year's Day, according to
OL,20,Fthe Sun.
