OL,6,FA Prison Service spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Police are investigating an assault
OL,8,Fon a prisoner at HMP Belmarsh on
OL,9,FJanuary 1. It would be inappropriate
OL,10,Fto comment further while they
OL,11,Finvestigate."
OL,13,FReports say Sharif suffered cuts to
OL,14,Fhis neck and face which he was treated
OL,15,Ffor inside the prison.
OL,17,FIt is understood he did not go to
OL,18,Fhospital.
