OL,6,FSharif was just weeks his minimum 40
OL,7,Fyear sentence for killing his daughter
OL,8,Falongside stepmother Beinash Batool,
OL,9,Fwho was sentenced to a minimum term of
OL,10,F33 years.
OL,12,FSara's uncle, Faisal Malik, 29, who
OL,13,Fwas found guilty of causing or
OL,14,Fallowing her death, was jailed for 16
OL,15,Fyears.
