OL,3,CFather of murdered schoolgirl Sara
OL,4,CSharif 'attacked in prison'
OL,6,FAt their sentencing at the Old Bailey,
OL,7,FMr Justice Cavanagh said Sara's death
OL,8,F"was the culmination of years of
OL,9,Fneglect, frequent assaults and what
OL,10,Fcan only be described as torture",
OL,11,Fmainly at the hands of Sharif.
OL,13,FThe senior judge said her "despicable
OL,14,Ftreatment" took place in "plain sight
OL,15,Fand in front of the rest of the
OL,16,Ffamily".
OL,18,FHe told Sharif: "You treated her in
OL,19,Fsuch a way because you considered it
OL,20,Fyour right to impose harsh discipline
OL,21,Fon her.
